Package com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth.authsub

Google's legacy AuthSub authorization as specified in AuthSub for Web Applications .

          Description

Class Summary
AuthSub  
AuthSubHelper AuthSub token manager for a single user.
AuthSubHelper.SessionTokenResponse Key/value data to parse a success response for an AuthSubSessionToken request.
AuthSubHelper.TokenInfoResponse Key/value data to parse a success response for an AuthSubTokenInfo request.
AuthSubSingleUseTokenRequestUrl Generic URL that builds an AuthSub request URL to retrieve a single-use token.
AuthSubSingleUseTokenRequestUrl.ResponseUrl Generic URL with a token parameter that can be used to extract the AuthSub single-use token from the AuthSubRequest response.
 

Package com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth.authsub Description

Google's legacy AuthSub authorization as specified in AuthSub for Web Applications .

This package depends on the com.google.api.client.auth, com.google.api.client.googleapis, com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth, com.google.api.client.http and com.google.api.client.util packages.

Warning: this package is experimental, and its content may be changed in incompatible ways or possibly entirely removed in a future version of the library
